
To run this example:

- Populate the db:

    node src/scripts/load_data.js


- Open the file src/examples/simple_oauth2_client/server.js
- Paste the id previously displayed in "client_id" value (search for 'TODO')


- Starts auth_server: 

    node src/server.js


- Starts the oauth2 client server:

  node src/examples/simple_oauth2_client/server.js


- Go to http://127.0.0.1:7070/ and try to log in
  Credentials: pruyssen@af83.com / 1234

To clear the sessions : just remove the cookies.

